lead_paragraph: Officials said the suspect fell six stories from an off-campus apartment building Tuesday morning, moments after he attacked a fellow student who was an acquaintance.

headline.print_headline: A Fatal Jump at Yale After a Stabbing
headline.main: Yale Student Jumps to His Death After He Stabbed Another, Police Say
